---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
const pageTitle = "Refund Policy | Free2AITools";
const pageDescription = "Refund Policy for Free2AITools API subscriptions.";
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 prose prose-invert prose-sm">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-black text-[var(--text-strong)] uppercase tracking-tight">Refund Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">Last updated: May 1, 2026</p>

    <h2>Free Tier</h2>
    <p>The Free tier (500 API calls/month) requires no payment and no refund applies.</p>

    <h2>Paid Subscriptions</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>14-day money-back guarantee</strong>: If you are not satisfied with your subscription, contact us within 14 days of your first payment for a full refund.</li>
      <li><strong>After 14 days</strong>: No refunds for the current billing period. You may cancel at any time, and your access continues until the end of the paid period.</li>
      <li><strong>Prorated refunds</strong>: If we discontinue a feature that was a primary reason for your subscription, we will offer a prorated refund for the remaining period.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to Request a Refund</h2>
    <p>Contact us via <a href="https://github.com/mosesy5688-cell/ai-nexus/issues">GitHub Issues</a> with your account email and reason for the refund. We will process refunds within 5-10 business days.</p>

    <h2>Chargebacks</h2>
    <p>Please contact us before initiating a chargeback with your bank. We are happy to resolve any issues directly. Chargebacks are handled by our payment processor (Merchant of Record).</p>
  </div>
</Layout>
